WWHF Offensive Maldocs in 2020

XLM Macros

    Simple Example:
    Open Excel -> Insert Sheet -> MS Excel 4.0 Macro
     - Formula: =EXEC("calc.exe")
     - Can also use process injection using Win32 API

Tools: 
    Excel4-DCOM - https://github.com/outflanknl/Excel4-DCOM
    SharpShooter - https://github.com/mdsecactivebreach/SharpShooter
    Macrome - https://github.com/michaelweber/Macrome
    EXCELntDonut - https://github.com/FortyNorthSecurity/EXCELntDonut

AV Evasion 
    Obfuscation - malware.pizza
    Very hidden excel tab - https://isc.sans.edu/forums/diary/Excel+Maldocs+Hidden+Sheets/25876/

Create XLM using .Net (No Metadata created & Compressed VBA Code)
